query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 tq1 s) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('18.04',
'command-line',
'discrete-mathematics',
'functions',
'galois-theory',
'graphing-functions',
'linear-algebra',
'logarithms',
'modular-arithmetic',
'number-theory',
'optimization',
'summation',
'system-installation',
'trigonometry',
'vector-spaces')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Autobiographer',
'Caucus',
'Constituent',
'Curious',
'Editor',
'Enthusiast',
'Excavator',
'Famous Question',
'Informed',
'Necromancer',
'Nice Question',
'Revival',
'Scholar',
'Student',
'Teacher') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
